00:00:07.970 --> 00:00:12.430
So Hamlet is either a 16h or 17th century
play, we’re not positive. The Tragedy of

00:00:12.430 --> 00:00:17.739
Hamlet, Prince of Denmark was written by William
Shakespeare sometime between 1599 and 1602

00:00:17.739 --> 00:00:21.659
and it’s considered by many to be Shakespeare’s
